<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <title>Exam Instructions | Pariksha</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="card glass-card p-5 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <span class="badge bg-primary-subtle text-primary mb-2"><%= exam.subject_name %></span>
                        <h2 class="fw-bold"><%= exam.exam_name %></h2>
                        <hr class="w-25 mx-auto">
                    </div>

                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>Important Instructions:</h5>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2 text-success"></i> Total Questions: <strong><%= qCount %></strong></li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2 text-success"></i> Time Limit: <strong><%= exam.duration_minutes %> Minutes</strong></li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="bi bi-check2 me-2 text-success"></i> Passing Marks: <strong><%= exam.pass_marks %> / <%= exam.total_marks %></strong></li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2 text-danger"></i> Do not refresh the page after starting the exam.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2 text-danger"></i> Ensure you have a stable internet connection.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                        <a href="/student/exam/<%= exam.exam_id %>/attempt" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg shadow">
                            I am Ready to Start <i class="bi bi-play-fill ms-2"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/student/dashboard" class="btn btn-link text-muted">Go Back to Dashboard</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>